them to stick in a red-hot umbrella...

02:13:49.298 --> 02:13:51.016
and open it wide!

02:13:52.093 --> 02:13:56.348
Man, you wanna get past the cops when
they start askin' about tonight?

02:13:56.722 --> 02:13:58.190
You play it cool.

