You wanna live in this lousy world?

02:17:00.561 --> 02:17:02.029
Play it cool.

02:17:02.938 --> 02:17:04.440
- I wanna get even!
- Get cool!

02:17:04.522 --> 02:17:06.025
- I wanna bust!
- Bust cool!

02:17:06.108 --> 02:17:08.236
- I wanna go!
- Go cool!

