♪ Boy, boy, crazy boy ♪

02:17:12.573 --> 02:17:14.620
♪ Get cool, boy ♪

02:17:15.242 --> 02:17:16.744
♪ Got a rocket ♪

02:17:16.826 --> 02:17:18.454
♪ In your pocket ♪

02:17:18.537 --> 02:17:21.005
♪ Keep cooly cool, boy ♪

