02:17:27.504 --> 02:17:29.974
♪ Take it slow, and daddy-o ♪

02:17:30.049 --> 02:17:32.643
♪ You can live it up and die in bed ♪

02:17:33.718 --> 02:17:36.313
♪ Boy, boy, crazy boy ♪

02:17:37.013 --> 02:17:39.016
♪ Stay loose, boy ♪

02:17:39.725 --> 02:17:42.945
♪ Breeze it, buzz it, easy does it ♪

02:17:43.020 --> 02:17:45.647
♪ Turn off the juice, boy ♪

02:17:45.731 --> 02:17:47.153
♪ Go, man, go ♪

02:17:47.233 --> 02:17:50.532
♪ But not like a yo-yo schoolboy ♪

02:17:50.945 --> 02:17:53.494
♪ Just play it cool, boy ♪

02:17:54.323 --> 02:17:56.165
♪ Real cool... ♪

