Easy, Action!

02:18:26.897 --> 02:18:29.116
Cool it, A-Rab, cool it!

02:18:31.235 --> 02:18:32.827
Go, cool!

02:18:35.755 --> 02:18:37.276
Pow!

02:18:46.291 --> 02:18:47.339
Go!

02:19:18.949 --> 02:19:20.075
Cool!

